experiments.name: NWB Visualization sample
experiments.description: This is a sample experiment to visualize an NWB file. The Neurodata without Borders – Neurophysiology initiative is a one-year project to produce a unified data format for cellular-based, neurophysiology data based on representative use cases initially from four laboratories – the Buzsaki group at NYU, the Svoboda group at Janelia Farm, the Meister group at Caltech, and the Allen Institute for Brain Science in Seattle.
